---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Future of Workforce" description="Explore how AI is reshaping real estate roles and the skills needed to thrive.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/10 to-dark">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">
        The Future of the Workforce
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        Artificial Intelligence isn't replacing real estate professionals—it's elevating them. Discover how brokers, asset managers, analysts, and leaders are evolving in an AI-integrated market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Sections -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Placeholder for content -->
    <div class="space-y-12">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">
          Evolving Roles in Commercial Real Estate
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Content coming soon. We're researching how specific roles in commercial real estate are transforming with AI integration.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-secondary pl-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">
          The Augmented Professional Mindset
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Learn about the skills, mindsets, and competencies that will define success in the next decade of real estate.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-l-4 border-accent pl-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 gradient-text">
          Reskilling and Career Opportunities
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Explore the pathways for real estate professionals to embrace AI as a tool for growth and innovation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-8 rounded-lg bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Key Topics</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary">→</span>
          <span>How broker responsibilities are shifting with AI tools</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary">→</span>
          <span>Asset managers leveraging predictive analytics</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary">→</span>
          <span>Analysts empowered by AI-driven insights</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary">→</span>
          <span>Leadership in the age of intelligent automation</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-primary/20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex justify-between">
      <a href="/CREFuture/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition">← Back Home</a>
      <a href="/CREFuture/transformation/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition">Next: Transformation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
